description:
If you are looking for casual puzzles games this collection is for you! 9 in 1 Puzzles is a collection of nine casual puzzles games. Simple and easy to play makes this collection a must have for every casual puzzle gamer. 

Features:
- 9 different puzzles games
- Easy and simple gameplay
- Unlockable skins
name: 9 in 1 Puzzles
intro: A collection of casual puzzles where everyone finds his favourite puzzle game!
